<Class name="CM_ProformaTransactionCriteria" id="2f17b0e5-70a4-4d4f-8af6-cb4db59cda74">
    <superclass name="CM_Object"/>
    <persistentAllowed/>
    <sharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassPersistentAllowed/>
    <subclassSharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <transientAllowed/>
    <text>

This class is used for CARGO proforma  configurations and VESSEL proforma configuration.


CARGO Proforma uses allCriteria, allTransactionTypes, myBank, myHookCode, myHookLink, myLocationHookCode, priority.
VESSEL Proforma uses allEventTypes, allHMSResources, myVessel, myBank, myHookCode, myHookLink, myLocationHookCode, priority.

</text>
